100.equation:
R0 = list()

R1 = R0
R1.append(14019)

R8 = R7
R8.append(12278)

R10 = sum(R9)
R11 = ('정국',R10)

R12 = list()
R12.append(R6)
R13 = R12
R13.append(R11)
R14 = R13

    max_name = R14[0][0]
    max_val = R14[0][1]
    for i in range(1,len(R14)):
        curr_name = R14[i][0]
        curr_val = R14[i][1]
        if curr_val > max_val:
            max_val = curr_val
            max_name = curr_name
    R15 = max_name

if type(R15) is float:

    if type(value) is str:
        if (idx > 0) and (type(R8[idx-1])) is str:
            min_seq = R8

R6 = R4

    min_val = R6[0][1]
    for i in range(1,len(R6)):

        curr_val = R6[i][1]
        if curr_val < min_val:
            min_val = curr_val
            min_name = curr_name
    R7 = min_name

    print(R7)

R2.append(R3)

R6 = R4
if type(R6[0]) == tuple:
    min_name = R6[0][0]
    min_val = R6[0][1]
    for i in range(1,len(R6)):
        curr_name = R6[i][0]
        curr_val = R6[i][1]
        if curr_val < min_val:
            min_val = curr_val
            min_name = curr_name
    R7 = min_name

min_seq = []
for idx, value in enumerate(R10):
    if type(value) is str:
        if (idx > 0) and (type(R10[idx-1])) is str:
            min_seq = R10
            break
        elif idx < len(R10)//2:
            min_seq = R10[len(R10)//2:]

            min_seq = R10[:len(R10)//2]
if min_seq == [] :

R11 = (min_seq * (int(93/len(min_seq)) + 1))[93-1]
if type(R11) is float:
    print('%.2f' % R11)
else:
    print(R11)
